claim.claim-text:
19. A method of removing a portable electronic device (PED) from a PED carrying case, comprising:
disposing a PED in a lift member of a PED compartment of a PED carrying case;
upwardly displacing a lift handle of the lift member;
upwardly displacing a lift cradle of the lift member;
upwardly displacing the PED relative to the PED compartment by the lift cradle; and
removing the PED from the lift member and the PED compartment.
